node.text:
Enough teaser clips, watch @georgerussell63 tackle one of the most fearsome circuits in the world 🤯

#Nordschleife #Nurburgring #HotLap #F1 #Formula1 #WeAreWilliams #WeAreRacing #WeAreFighting #GR63 #NL6

node.title: George takes Aleix for a high-speed ride around the Nordschleife!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Williams Racing in Autodromo Nazionale Monza with @georgerussell63. May be an image of one or more people and people standing.

node.text:
This weekend is far from over. Bring on tomorrow 💪

Let us know how you think we'll get on in Sprint Qualifying! 🏃‍♂️

#WeAreWilliams #F1 #Formula1

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Williams Racing in Autodromo Nazionale Monza with @nicholaslatifi, and @georgerussell63. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text:
Quali complete. @georgerussell63  will start P15 tomorrow with @nicholaslatifi just behind in P16 👊

All still to play for at Monza. We'll be ready to push forward during Sprint Qualifying 💪

#WeAreWilliams #F1 #Formula1

Russell Vision 👁️

🎥 @f1 

#WeAreWilliams #F1 #Formula1

node.text:
THE TEMPLE OF SPEED ⚡️

Gaining its nickname due to its long straights that produce some of the fastest racing on the calendar, punctuated by numerous chicanes and sweeping turns, the 5.793km layout blasts its way through a stunning parkland setting on the outskirts of one of Europe’s fashion capitals 🇮🇹

Where does Monza rank amongst your favourite tracks? 👀

#WeAreWilliams #F1 #Formula1
